   [coamail.gif]
   Albuquerque Housing Services (AHS), is a division of the City of
   Albuquerque's Department of Family and Community Services. AHS has been
   providing housing assistance to low income citizens of Albuquerque
   since 1967. Our purpose is to help people find safe and decent housing.
   We strive to provide living environments which promote economic and
   social diversity and upward mobility.

Check us out, we're here to help!

